articles.title: Renesas Rad-Hard ICs Power Japan's First Moon Lander - Eetasia.com
articles.description: Renesas' rad-hard ICs were onboard Japan's SLIM spacecraft that successfully touched down on the Moon's low latitude area on January 20.
